  "title": "Litro increases LP gas prices",
  "body_lines": [
    "Litro Gas Lanka Limited has increased the price of its 12.5kg liquefied petroleum (LP) gas cylinder by Rs. 2,185.",
    "The price hike will come into effect from midnight today (April 26).",
    "Accordingly, the revised price of a 12.5kg LP gas cylinder now stands at Rs. 4,860."
  ],
  "translate": {
